title: Chip Tunes Suxx
info:
Dedicated to scenemusic.eu repertoire. I tired of listening to a loud blip-blops based on primitive chord progressions and stupid vocal tunes on Scene Radio. So, eat my protest! :)
Released at chiptune compo [b]ChipYxa#7[/b] ( [url]http://www.chiptown.ru/chipyxa7/[/url] ), 100Kb-compo.
